# AI Adoption Opportunity Project
## AI-assisted Strategy Monitoring in Public Sector / Federal Agencies

**Bootcamp:** Ironhack AI Consulting Bootcamp — Project 5
**Week:** 8
**Sector:** Public Sector / Bundesagentur
**Company Size:** Large (200+ employees)

---

## Business Question
> "Can AI help a federal agency monitor strategy progress continuously — instead of flying blind until the annual review?"

## Use Case
AI-supported KPI monitoring layer that aggregates departmental inputs, detects deviations from strategic targets, and delivers automated early-warning signals to leadership.

