## Setup
```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run dashboard/dashboard.py
```

## Dataset
IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition (Kaggle)
Used as structural proxy for organizational performance variance.
Limitation: US-based, synthetic — documented in use_case_discovery.md

